tourBios.carHigh:
2013: Finished T120 at the Qualifying Tournament to earn his Web.com Tour playing privileges...Played 12 events on the Adams Pro Tour, making eight cuts. Won twice (Coca-Cola Walmart Open and the Bay Oaks Golf Open) and posted three other top-10s2012: Continued on the Adams Pro Tour, playing in 12 events.

2011: Was the Adams Pro Tour Player of the Year.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Qualified for the U.S. Amateur three straight years (2003-06), Was named University of Texas-Arlington Athlete of the Year in 2005, was Southland Conference Athlete of the Year in 2006 and an NCAA Academic All-American in 2008
tourBios.personal: Favorite pro team is the Texas Rangers... Favorite quote is "Whatever it takes; no excuses."... Wants to attend a Major League Baseball game at every team's stadium... Keeps Clif bars and beef jerky in his golf bag... If he were not playing golf he would be a meteorologist..
